## Requirements

Please implement the `processUserProfile` method in the `DataProcessingService` class. This method receives an XML-formatted string containing user profile data and must use JAXB to deserialize it into a `com.example.datamodel.model.UserProfile` object and return it. If the input XML is malformed or cannot be parsed, the method should handle exceptions appropriately.

## Technology Stack

