## Implementation Requirements

- Package name: `com.example.datamodel.service`
- Class name: `DataProcessingService`
- Method signature: `public com.example.datamodel.model.UserProfile processUserProfile(java.lang.String xmlData)`
- Core logic: Use `JAXBContext` to create an `Unmarshaller` instance and invoke its `unmarshal` method to convert the XML string into a `UserProfile` object.
- Appropriate exception handling is required
- Code should be concise and efficient


